  "title": "绘制概念图是否涉及内隐提取练习？",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"QlBZnl0z\">按理说，我会预期绘制概念图这项活动能触发<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zQGck6tJtxXKa79HWtsV9LT\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">内隐提取练习</a><sup data-text=\"内隐提取练习\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1928747456914515370\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>，然而 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zFUBZG5yY1aKJ4hpak2jWPA\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Karpicke 与 Blunt (2011) 的研究</a>发现事实并非如此，Kornell (2012) 的研究也得出了同样的结论（该研究被 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zV1xNteVY4otyHP5gCcanVN\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Agarwal 等人 (2021) 在其系统性综述中所引用</a>）。</p><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"HvaxwZ-D\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1928747456914515370\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">内隐提取练习</a></li><li data-pid=\"FulBiVtQ\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1930200421491803500\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">绘制概念图</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"a1kSLiu9\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"Yu6lrJBQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 gemini-2.5-pro，校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z3J3QxG3TkZfqkKWTx9cBvi\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Does concept mapping involve implicit retrieval practice?</a></blockquote>",
